extendedInfo.description: York Hospital is a not-for-profit health system on the southern coast  of Maine - A modern facility with excellent medical/surgical units, an  outstanding emergent care center, innovative breast care program and  extensive inpatient and outpatient services that delivers stellar care  for every patient.  York Hospital's mobile app delivers rapid anywhere  access to all of York's care doctors, services and locations, a 24  hour nurse advice line, online prescription refills and informaton  about York's quality and safety.
